                           <p>Quires start with the fleshside. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Hair side and flesh side of folios distinguishable. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Large square initial words. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Chapter titles are given in Latin in the margins. </p>
                           
                           
                           
